{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Hypertext (ハイパーテキスト)","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Hypertext","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>ハイパーテキストは、ほかのテキストへのリンクを含むテキストであり、小説のように単一で線形の流れのものとは対照的なものです。</p>\n\n<p>この用語は、テッド・ネルソンによって 1965年に造られました。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_more","title":"詳細情報","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_knowledge","title":"一般知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>ウィキペディアの<a title=\"ハイパーテキスト\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/ハイパーテキスト\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ハイパーテキスト</a>の記事</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"technical_reference","title":"技術リファレンス","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"http://www.ualberta.ca/dept/chemeng/AIX-43/share/man/info/C/a_doc_lib/aixuser/aix6kdov/hyperv1aix.htm\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Hypertext Information Base</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"詳細情報","id":"learn_more"}],"summary":"ハイパーテキストは、ほかのテキストへのリンクを含むテキストであり、小説のように単一で線形の流れのものとは対照的なものです。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Hypertext","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Hipertexto","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Hypertexte","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Hipertekst","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Гипертекст","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Hypertext","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/hypertext","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/hypertext/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Hypertext","title":"Hypertext (ハイパーテキスト)"}],"pageTitle"